XML-XParent

This package provides a way to store an XML document in a DBMS 
XParent schema.
The package provide scripts to load an XML document into 
the DBMS and perform queries on it.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc XML::XParent

